{"tid":1186690,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"養生？","createTime":"2019-06-05T06:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T12:27:39.000Z","uid":76885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"76c1c6116a35dea64e9d9745c20c5ccd9b800585","tid":1186690,"uid":76885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:04:33.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇左套紀錄片。<br />\n<em>百歲人瑞長壽村</em>：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.books.com.tw/products/D020062816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2FD020062816&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKLyLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=84f70e45\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.books.com.tw/products/D020062816</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>本片走訪日本、美國、義大利和法國，揭長壽秘訣；<br />\n以飲食，基因，居住地，生活方式等各種因素，探討人瑞形成的各種可能性。</em><br />\n<br />\n其實無咩特別既Point？<br />\n健康飲食。運動。好既基因。信仰。人際關係。<br />\n<br />\n其中兩點有趣既係：<br />\n1. 法國專家估2005年後出世既女仔，每兩個人有一個會係百歲人瑞。<br />\n2. 對長壽者而言，重要既係搵到目標同自己既價值。<br />\n<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n好奇，你有無留意開d咩養生既野？<br />\n西方科學角度？定中醫角度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ce22fabc5f18ee222bc4d1e631acaf3ef80394","tid":1186690,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:11:50.000Z","msg":"男人要養生，精子要定期推陳出新"},{"pid":"18219a944983e06ff830a7e71bd5b23d86a3194a","tid":1186690,"uid":76885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:16:57.000Z","msg":"相關既野，睇過有印象既：<br />\n<br />\n1<br />\n<em>The Telomere Effect: A Revolutionary Approach to Living Younger, Healthier, Longer</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Telomere-Effect-Revolutionary-Approach-Healthier/dp/1455587974\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FTelomere-Effect-Revolutionary-Approach-Healthier%2Fdp%2F1455587974&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKLyLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=93b1334a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Telomere-Effect-Revolutionary-Approach-Healthier/dp/1455587974</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://readmoo.com/book/210077032000101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freadmoo.com%2Fbook%2F210077032000101&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKLyLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=202b574b\" target=\"_blank\">https://readmoo.com/book/210077032000101</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>作者諾貝爾生理醫學獎得主伊莉莎白．布雷克本，<br />\n長期鑽研端粒現象與效應。她發現：<br />\n端粒（telomere）是染色體的末端，也是染色體的保護箍。<br />\n正是端粒的長短，控制了細胞和人體的壽命；<br />\n而且端粒不只是會執行遺傳指令，還會聽從你的指示，<br />\n也就是說，你的生活方式等同於對你的端粒下令，<br />\n讓你細胞老化得更快或更慢一點。</em><br />\n<br />\n睇目錄好似都大概知本書大概會講咩？<br />\n<br />\n細胞早衰，會讓你身心都衰老<br />\n細胞正在傾聽<ins>你的思維</ins><br />\n了解自己的<ins>壓力反應</ins>模式<br />\n壓力如何侵入細胞？<br />\n如何減少「自我威脅」的壓力<br />\n<ins>負面思想、彈性思維</ins>，如何影響你的端粒？<br />\n<ins>自我同情</ins>，讓自己喘息一下<br />\n你的<ins>個性</ins>如何影響你的壓力反應？<br />\n讓<ins>憂鬱和焦慮</ins>不上身<br />\n三分鐘呼吸練習法<br />\n<ins>減壓技巧</ins>有益於端粒健康<br />\n訓練你的端粒：<ins>運動</ins>量要多少才足夠？<br />\n<ins>良好睡眠</ins>，可讓疲憊的端粒回復活力<br />\n何者有益端粒：減重？還是健康的<ins>新陳代謝</ins>？<br />\n駕馭你對<ins>糖</ins>的渴望<br />\n怎麼<ins>吃</ins>，對端粒和細胞的健康最好？<br />\n<ins>人際關係和社區環境</ins>對端粒的影響<br />\n盡可能遠離<ins>有毒物質</ins><br />\n<ins>童年</ins>會影響一生：幼年生活如何形塑端粒？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n<em>Ikigai: The Japanese Secret to a Long and Happy Life</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Ikigai-Japanese-Secret-Long-Happy/dp/0143130722/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FIkigai-Japanese-Secret-Long-Happy%2Fdp%2F0143130722%2F&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKLyLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=66e8727d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Ikigai-Japanese-Secret-Long-Happy/dp/0143130722/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://playlifecloud.com/201807-ikigai-%E3%80%8C%E7%94%9F%E3%81%8D%E7%94%B2%E6%96%90%E3%80%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplaylifecloud.com%2F201807-ikigai-%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%2594%259F%25E3%2581%258D%25E7%2594%25B2%25E6%2596%2590%25E3%2580%258D%2F&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKLyLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=381a2f72\" target=\"_blank\">http://playlifecloud.com/201807-ikigai-%E3%80%8C%E7%94%9F%E3%81%8D%E7%94%B2%E6%96%90%E3%80%8D/</a><br />\n在日文中有個詞彙，叫做「生き甲斐」，中文可以翻成「生命的意義」，英文可以解讀為「The reason for living」。 日本人相信每個人都有自己的ikigai，才會活得幸福快樂、活得長久。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/playlifecloud.com/wp-content/uploads/ikigai-1.0.png?w=1310\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fplaylifecloud.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fikigai-1.0.png%3Fw%3D1310&h=59df76cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一、找到自己享受的事情：興趣<br />\n二、找到自己擅長的事情：天賦<br />\n三、可以用來吃飯的技能：專長<br />\n四、滿足這個世界的需求：需求<br />\n<br />\n這四點重複的項目，就是你人生的價值所在。<br />\n<br />\nOther：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%9F%A5%E6%80%A7%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F/104398/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%93%B2%E5%AD%B8-%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84ikigai%E5%97%8E-%E5%BE%9E%E5%BF%99%E7%A2%8C%E7%99%BC%E6%8E%98%E5%BF%AB%E6%A8%82%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%9D%BF%E6%99%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%2F104398%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%2593%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E6%2589%25BE%25E5%2588%25B0%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E7%259A%2584ikigai%25E5%2597%258E-%25E5%25BE%259E%25E5%25BF%2599%25E7%25A2%258C%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%258E%2598%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E6%25A8%2582%25E6%2589%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%259D%25BF%25E6%2599%25BA&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKLyLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=e6855491\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%9F%A5%E6%80%A7%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F/104398/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E5%93%B2%E5%AD%B8-%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84ikigai%E5%97%8E-%E5%BE%9E%E5%BF%99%E7%A2%8C%E7%99%BC%E6%8E%98%E5%BF%AB%E6%A8%82%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E7%9D%BF%E6%99%BA</a>"},{"pid":"89a92a7c077aeaebd3cb9ab2345eb57977738750","tid":1186690,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:18:59.000Z","msg":"老人家生存有兩樣野好緊要<br />\n1. goals<br />\n2. community <br />\nGoals 即係指你老年生存有咩目標, 有咩想做 (假設你已經唔駛再養兒育女)<br />\n由環遊全世界到日日行下山種下花都得. 總之比自己有目標, 有野想做.<br />\ncommunity