n<br />\n情緒影響免疫系統。<br />\n影響內分泌，譬如hormone。<br />\n<br />\n情緒影響行為。<br />\n譬如飲食、睡眠。<br />\n<br />\n影響社交。<br />\n<br />\n前者係直接，後兩者間接，而三者都影響身體健康。<br />\n<br />\n而精神健康本身就係健康一部分。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:18:07.000Z","msg":"點可以保持精神健康？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T12:27:39.000Z","msg":"How to look after your mental health<br />\n<em><a href=\"https://www.mentalhealth.org.uk/publications/how-to-mental-health\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mentalhealth.org.uk%2Fpublications%2Fhow-to-mental-health&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKLyLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=40c6aff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mentalhealth.org.uk/publications/how-to-mental-health</a></em><br />\n<br />\n1. Talk about your feelings<br />\n2. Keep active<br />\n3. Eat well<br />\n4. Drink sensibly<br />\n5. Keep in touch<br />\n6. Ask for help<br />\n7. Take a break<br />\n8. Do something you&rsquo;re good at<br />\n9. Accept who you are<br />\n10. Care for others<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}